<h1>Disbursement of VA Benefits</h1>
<p>Disbursement of veteran benefit awards usually will not occur until at least a month after the start of a semester. Many VA awards take up to two months after the start of the semester to disburse. This estimate is regardless of how early the student completed the requirements for the award.</p>
<h2>VA Forms</h2>
<p>These forms are only to be completed and submitted with consultation and recommendation from the VA Benefits Coordinator. Contact the VA Benefits Coordinator with any questions or concerns regarding these forms.</p>
