<h2>Late fees</h2>
<p>BYU-Idaho is flexible with waiving late fees for students who are eligible for the Post 9/11 - Chapter 33 GI Bill. The <a href="http://www.byui.edu/financial-services" title="Link to the Financial Services page">Bursars Office</a> maintains a list (supplied by VA Coordinators at the Financial Aid Office) of eligible students awaiting Chapter 33 GI Bill benefits. Despite if a student has waived late fees, the late fee charge will still display on a student's <a href="https://dep.byui.edu/PersonalAccounts/AccountInfo/personalAccounts.aspx" title="Link to Personal Account Summary">Personal Account Summary</a> until the VA Benefit is released and covers the charges.</p>
